FBIS4-58899 "drnes089_s_94009" FBIS-NES-94-089 Daily Report 7 May 1994 Iran Foreign Ministry Condemns Interference in Yemen Foreign Ministry Condemns Interference in Yemen LD0705150194 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in Persian 1430 GMT 7 May 94 LD0705150194 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] Iran has expressed deep regret about internal clashes in Yemen. A spokesman of our country's Foreign Ministry today called on the warring sides in Yemen to maintain their self-control, observe Islamic principles, and find peaceful ways to solve their differences. He also condemned foreign interference in the escalation of crisis in Yemen and announced the readiness of the Islamic Republic of Iran to help towards solving the differences and maintaining the Yemen unity.
